      "id": "PopularPost83152",
      "post_content": "Uh, that's quite the creative name. \"Vigilance - gives vigilance.\" Wowee.\n  \n   \nBecause of this, I think Vigilance should *actually* be keyworded as \"[Eternal Warrior](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eternal Warrior).\" Trample should be [Primal Frenzy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Primal Frenzy); First Strike should be [Lance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lance). And of course, who could deny the awesome might of the [Mountain Goat](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mountain Goat), with its awe-inspiring [Burrowing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burrowing) powers. That's right, a burrowing mountain goat.\n  \n   \nTremble in fear.",
      "posted_by": "Kirbster",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost83152\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Uh, that's quite the creative name. \"Vigilance - gives vigilance.\" Wowee.\r<br/> <br/>Because of this, I think Vigilance should <i>actually</i> be keyworded as \"<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Eternal Warrior\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eternal Warrior\">Eternal Warrior</a>.\" Trample should be <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Primal Frenzy\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Primal Frenzy\">Primal Frenzy</a>; First Strike should be <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lance\">Lance</a>. And of course, who could deny the awesome might of the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mountain Goat\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mountain Goat\">Mountain Goat</a>, with its awe-inspiring <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Burrowing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burrowing\">Burrowing</a> powers. That's right, a burrowing mountain goat.\r<br/> <br/>Tremble in fear.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '83152'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy37159\">Kirbster</span>\r\n                                (6/29/2010 10:24:07 PM)\r\n           